279
00:17:51,204 --> 00:17:52,674
Come on!

280
00:17:55,143 --> 00:17:57,244
I don't understand why you're doing this to me.

281
00:18:02,214 --> 00:18:03,552
She stole my phone.

282
00:18:03,553 --> 00:18:04,883
And you ask me why I need it?

283
00:18:05,754 --> 00:18:07,293
Whether I need it today or tomorrow,

284
00:18:07,294 --> 00:18:08,352
