286
00:18:11,823 --> 00:18:15,264
I didn't steal it. I've acquired a lost item.

287
00:18:21,873 --> 00:18:23,674
Okay. Fine.

288
00:18:25,143 --> 00:18:27,944
I guess you picked up the phone that I lost.

289
00:18:28,573 --> 00:18:29,613
And?

290
00:18:30,313 --> 00:18:32,484
I fell down by myself.

291
00:18:32,684 --> 00:18:34,484
I fell by myself. All right?

292
00:18:35,313 --> 00:18:38,083
Now you know. Give me my phone back.

293
00:18:39,653 --> 00:18:40,853
If you make...

294
00:18:42,093 --> 00:18:45,024
a statement different from this during the investigation,

295
00:18:46,494 --> 00:18:47,733
my client...

296
00:18:47,734 --> 00:18:50,363
will testify about what she saw on this phone.

297
00:18:53,803 --> 00:18:55,073
You must have seen them.

298
00:18:56,774 --> 00:18:58,004
Are you interested in any of them?

299
00:18:59,613 --> 00:19:01,573
- Excuse me? - Do you want to buy one?

300
00:19:02,944 --> 00:19:04,044
If not, whatever.

301
00:19:06,143 --> 00:19:08,984
Tell her to avoid me.

302
00:19:35,714 --> 00:19:36,743
Yes.

303
00:19:36,744 --> 00:19:38,613
I've recently acquired a phone,

304
00:19:39,583 --> 00:19:41,312
and I found illegal videos on it.

305
00:19:41,313 --> 00:19:43,653
(Unknown: Welcome back.)

306
00:19:55,264 --> 00:19:58,563
(Seokyung Station, 1-39)

307
00:20:01,274 --> 00:20:05,474
(Unknown)

308
00:20:10,784 --> 00:20:13,754
The number you have dialled is out of service.

309
00:20:14,214 --> 00:20:16,984
Please recheck the number and call again.

310
00:20:17,083 --> 00:20:18,954
The number you have dialled is...

311
00:20:32,434 --> 00:20:33,603
By the way,

312
00:20:34,073 --> 00:20:36,372
why do you keep refusing to meet with your lawyer?

313
00:20:36,373 --> 00:20:38,473
You punk. He's not my lawyer.

314
00:20:38,474 --> 00:20:40,474
He stabbed me in the back.

315
00:20:41,944 --> 00:20:45,684
I have so much quality information...

316
00:20:46,083 --> 00:20:48,014
that people keep looking for me.

317
00:20:49,484 --> 00:20:52,183
You're our boss for a reason.

318
00:20:52,184 --> 00:20:53,224
That's amazing, boss!

319
00:20:54,393 --> 00:20:55,593
Let go.

320
00:20:56,093 --> 00:20:57,294
It must be snacks.

321
00:21:08,934 --> 00:21:10,103
What's this?

322
00:21:10,944 --> 00:21:12,902
