528
00:38:13,335 --> 00:38:15,503
Make yourself at home until your living situation gets sorted out.

529
00:38:15,504 --> 00:38:17,705
I'll go sleep somewhere else if you want me to.

530
00:38:19,004 --> 00:38:20,044
What about you?

531
00:38:21,614 --> 00:38:23,645
Do you like magic?

532
00:38:24,785 --> 00:38:26,015
No, not really.

533
00:38:27,185 --> 00:38:28,714
It is deception, after all.

534
00:38:38,864 --> 00:38:40,634
You will learn to like it.

535
00:38:44,504 --> 00:38:46,165
Let me show you some magic too.

536
00:38:54,314 --> 00:38:55,314
Hey.

537
00:38:58,145 --> 00:38:59,145
Yes.

538
00:38:59,314 --> 00:39:00,754
Another lawyer is here.

539
00:39:07,955 --> 00:39:08,994
I...

540
00:39:08,995 --> 00:39:10,424
I won't settle.

